<h2 id="updating-the-supabase-cli" class="group scroll-mt-24">Updating the Supabase CLI<a href="#updating-the-supabase-cli" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition"><span aria-hidden="true">#</span></a></h2>
<p>When a new <a href="https://github.com/supabase/cli/releases">version</a> is released, you can update the CLI using the same methods.</p>
